Package: C3PO
Type: Package
Title: C implementation of the R package R2D2
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Mathieu", "Vrac", email = "mathieu.vrac@lsce.ipsl.fr", role = c("aut")),
             person("Soulivanh", "Thao", email = "soulivanh.thao@lsce.ipsl.fr", role = c("ctr", "cre")))
Description: This package provides the c3po function 
  which uses the R C interface to implement the
  multivariate bias-correction method, R2D2, presented in Vrac(2018)).
  Vrac, M.: Multivariate bias adjustment of high-dimensional climate simulations:
  the Rank Resampling for Distributions and Dependences (R2D2) bias correction,
  Hydrol. Earth Syst. Sci., 22, 3175â€“3196,
  https://doi.org/10.5194/hess-22-3175-2018, 2018.
